[32m+[m[32m- **fix(startup) #369**: Unify env loading across `npm run start`, `run-standalone.mjs`, and Electron to respect `DATA_DIR/.env → ~/.omniroute/.env → ./.env` priority — prevents generating a new `STORAGE_ENCRYPTION_KEY` over an existing encrypted database[m
