[32m+[m[32m### ✨ New Features (PRs #363 & #365)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **feat(docs):** integrate multi-page documentation into OmniRoute dashboard (#1969)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **feat(settings):** add request body limit setting (#1968)[m
