[32m+[m[32m- **fix(db):** resolve legacy encryption fallback causing re-encryption loops (#1941)[m
[32m+[m[32m- **fix(auth):** fix Codex assistant final_answer response sanitization (#1965)[m
[32m+[m
[32m+[m[32m- **feat(providers):** Implement Image Generation and Editing capabilities for ChatGPT Web, including in-band chat image generation and caching (#1606).[m
