[32m+[m[32m- **Strict-Random Routing Strategy**: Fisher-Yates shuffle deck with anti-repeat guarantee and mutex serialization for concurrent requests. Independent decks per combo and per provider.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **API Key Access Controls**: `allowedConnections` (restrict which connections a key can use), `is_active` (enable/disable key with 403), `accessSchedule` (time-based access control), `autoResolve` toggle, rename keys via PATCH.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Connection Groups**: Group provider connections by environment. Accordion view in Limits page with localStorage persistence and smart auto-switch.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **External Pricing Sync (LiteLLM)**: 3-tier pricing resolution (user overrides → synced → defaults). Opt-in via `PRICING_SYNC_ENABLED=true`. MCP tool `omniroute_sync_pricing`. 23 new tests.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **i18n**: 30 languages updated with strict-random strategy, API key management strings. pt-BR fully translated.[m
